items.title: Classified Venezuela briefing leaves lawmakers split along party lines after Maduro capture
items.description: Senate Democrats are moving to force a vote on a measure to block further military action in Venezuela.

items.title: Maduro says he was 'kidnapped' and is 'prisoner of war' in New York court, pleads not guilty
items.description: Nicolas Maduro and his wife, Cilia Flores, were captured on Saturday by U.S. forces in Venezuela on the orders of President Donald Trump.
